Class CommonUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.graql.internal.util.CommonUtil

  • public class CommonUtil
extends Object
    Common utility methods used within Graql. Some of these methods are Graql-specific, others add important "missing" methods to Java/Guava classes.
